{"tid":945044,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"楊格：曼聯在遏制著利物浦，但折射讓他們贏了","createTime":"2018-12-17T14:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T15:41:57.000Z","uid":124292,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ae71a9cc363fb080eb170a8615e16033377f309d","tid":945044,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T14:34:06.000Z","msg":"賽後在接受球會官方電視台採訪時，楊格透露了隊友們的心情並感謝了遠赴客場的紅魔球迷的支持。<br />\n<br />\n「球迷們很棒，整個賽季都是。比賽對他們來講很失望，對我們也是一樣。我們要努力延續在比賽中積極的方面，為下一場比賽做好準備。」<br />\n<br />\n「很失望，除此之外我覺得我們能說的並不多，當然了，兩個折射。但我們1-1追平的時候我們也感覺我們可以繼續並且贏下比賽，但最終沒有。」<br />\n<br />\n「當然失球總是令人失望的，我覺得我們在遏制著他們，下半場壓力很大，我們也預料到了。我不覺得利物浦可以進球，但兩個折射球，打在我們身上折射進了，然後他們就贏得了比賽。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/man-utd-young-liverpool-news-15560395\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.manchestereveningnews.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Ffootball-news%2Fman-utd-young-liverpool-news-15560395&d=QfCtq%2FJ5M8ChdtAMCkZiHZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=39a07e12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/man-utd-young-liverpool-news-15560395</a>"},{"pid":"959b0be4dfbcd6dbe5ec7989f2f75e400a4ea20c","tid":945044,"uid":4706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T14:34:54.000Z","msg":"平行時空<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"904b3721954b058305e3f396f0ad09fd3798cb0b","tid":945044,"uid":3743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T14:35:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50c74068a257a117f4583b8d0c6892